>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
*> 30ORDBE0 — documents: file access for the DOCORDNB indexed file
*> (document_ordnungsbegriff). Ops: BYDC (table for a document — the
*> boundary sorts by type+value) · WRT. L-RET: 00 · 22 · 9x.
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. "30ORDBE0".
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT ORDB-FILE ASSIGN TO "DOCORDNB"
        ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
        ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC
        RECORD KEY IS OB-ID
        ALTERNATE RECORD KEY IS OB-DOC WITH DUPLICATES
        LOCK MODE IS AUTOMATIC
        FILE STATUS IS WS-FS.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD ORDB-FILE.
COPY "30ORDBR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==OB==.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-FS                PIC X(2).
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 L-OP                 PIC X(4).
01 L-RET                PIC X(2).
COPY "30ORDBR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==L-OB==.
01 L-OB-TABLE.
   05 L-OB-COUNT        PIC 9(4).
   05 L-OB-ROW OCCURS 50.
      10 L-OB-ROW-TYPE  PIC X(100).
      10 L-OB-ROW-VALUE PIC X(200).
PROCEDURE DIVISION USING L-OP L-RET L-OB-REC L-OB-TABLE.
MAIN.
    PERFORM OPEN-FILE
    IF L-RET NOT = "00"
        GOBACK
    END-IF
    EVALUATE L-OP
        WHEN "BYDC" PERFORM DO-BY-DOC
        WHEN "WRT " PERFORM DO-WRITE
        WHEN OTHER  MOVE "99" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE
    CLOSE ORDB-FILE
    GOBACK.

OPEN-FILE.
    MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    OPEN I-O ORDB-FILE
    IF WS-FS = "35"
        OPEN OUTPUT ORDB-FILE
        CLOSE ORDB-FILE
        OPEN I-O ORDB-FILE
    END-IF
    IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "05"
        MOVE "91" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-BY-DOC.
    MOVE 0 TO L-OB-COUNT
    MOVE L-OB-DOC TO OB-DOC
    START ORDB-FILE KEY IS = OB-DOC
    IF WS-FS = "00"
        PERFORM UNTIL L-OB-COUNT >= 50
            READ ORDB-FILE NEXT
            IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "02"
                EXIT PERFORM
            END-IF
            IF OB-DOC NOT = L-OB-DOC
                EXIT PERFORM
            END-IF
            ADD 1 TO L-OB-COUNT
            MOVE OB-TYPE  TO L-OB-ROW-TYPE (L-OB-COUNT)
            MOVE OB-VALUE TO L-OB-ROW-VALUE (L-OB-COUNT)
        END-PERFORM
    END-IF
    MOVE "00" TO L-RET.

DO-WRITE.
    MOVE L-OB-REC TO OB-REC
    WRITE OB-REC
    EVALUATE WS-FS
        WHEN "00" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "02" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "22" MOVE "22" TO L-RET
        WHEN OTHER MOVE "92" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE.
END PROGRAM "30ORDBE0".
